Is there an event coming up? Is it your first one? You keep hearing about &quot;1 billion crop row&quot; but don't know what it means? This is the place for you!

[b]What is an event?[/b]
[s]An event is a specific period of time that usually coincide with a major US holiday like Halloween, Christmas, easter etc.... The developer [user]Firestream[/user] wants it to be a fun time and gives out some bonuses and usually some limited time quests[/s]